<div class="header">
<a class="title" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/commit/e42fc6263379176869dd9a6467e37f9956d56431">avcodec/mobiclip: Fix heap-buffer-overflow</a>
</div>
<div class="title_text">
<table class="object_header">
<tr><td>author</td><td><a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/e42fc6263379176869dd9a6467e37f9956d56431?s=Andreas+Rheinhardt;st=author" title="Search for commits authored by Andreas Rheinhardt">Andreas Rheinhardt</a> <a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/e42fc6263379176869dd9a6467e37f9956d56431?s=andreas.rheinhardt@gmail.com;st=author" title="Search for commits authored by andreas.rheinhardt@gmail.com">&lt;andreas.rheinhardt@gmail.com&gt;</a></td><td rowspan="2"></td></tr>
<tr><td></td><td><span class="datetime">Tue, 15 Sep 2020 01:03:18 +0000</span> (<span class="atnight">03:03</span> +0200)</td></tr>
<tr><td>committer</td><td><a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/e42fc6263379176869dd9a6467e37f9956d56431?s=Andreas+Rheinhardt;st=committer" title="Search for commits committed by Andreas Rheinhardt">Andreas Rheinhardt</a> <a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/e42fc6263379176869dd9a6467e37f9956d56431?s=andreas.rheinhardt@gmail.com;st=committer" title="Search for commits committed by andreas.rheinhardt@gmail.com">&lt;andreas.rheinhardt@gmail.com&gt;</a></td><td rowspan="2"></td></tr>
<tr><td></td><td><span class="datetime">Tue, 15 Sep 2020 17:25:26 +0000</span> (19:25 +0200)</td></tr>
</table></div>
<div class="page_body">
<div class="log">
The&nbsp;MobiClip&nbsp;decoder&nbsp;uses&nbsp;adjacent&nbsp;pixels&nbsp;for&nbsp;prediction;&nbsp;yet&nbsp;when<br/>
accessing&nbsp;the&nbsp;left&nbsp;pixel,&nbsp;it&nbsp;was&nbsp;forgotten&nbsp;to&nbsp;clip&nbsp;the&nbsp;x&nbsp;coordinate.<br/>
This&nbsp;results&nbsp;in&nbsp;an&nbsp;heap-buffer-overflow.&nbsp;It&nbsp;can&nbsp;e.g.&nbsp;be&nbsp;reproduced&nbsp;with<br/>
the&nbsp;sample&nbsp;from&nbsp;https://samples.ffmpeg.org/V-codecs/MOHD/crap.avi&nbsp;when<br/>
forcing&nbsp;the&nbsp;video&nbsp;decoder&nbsp;to&nbsp;mobiclip.<br/>
<br/>
<span class="signoff">Reviewed-by: Paul B Mahol &lt;onemda@gmail.com&gt;</span><br/>
<span class="signoff">Signed-off-by: Andreas Rheinhardt &lt;andreas.rheinhardt@gmail.com&gt;</span><br/>
</div>
